本研發產品。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不惜工本 = 抄人地 design 慳咗一大筆，淨返係用血汗工廠生產，要幾多成本？<br />\n而且，仲未計封鎖市場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"你講緊apple?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我剩係知apple會做埋呢d賤野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"真係唔知咩牌子手機抄垃圾M額"},{"pid":"19ab8d3e86c525e59526a9ffdccfbb0e6bfd2583","tid":904751,"uid":181294,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c2e4506e6ad13dc20899563c5bfedfe4a2000e6","tid":904751,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19ab8d3e86c525e59526a9ffdccfbb0e6bfd2583","tid":904751,"uid":181294,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"539a7aa99034539ff157a864b7299fa6ace17db3","tid":904751,"uid":30067,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"假如huawei係日本牌子+日本制造+日本研發<br />\nP20 Mate20 肯定捧到上天<br />\n到時android 唔會推介samsung nokia op<br />\n全連登版版都係huawei"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"Sharp係大陸牌子好耐了"},{"pid":"9f04227eaf5946221e7aa1b3289052c5fdde7cd7","tid":904751,"uid":181294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8df4a60987b3a44ddb83beee0b6ac3de9a5f4fa6","tid":904751,"uid":1086,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"sony仲有人用？"},{"pid":"1d064367d31c80e438aa332cf30530d04b5b04af","tid":904751,"uid":44569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"日本人都唔多用 sony"},{"pid":"90c3cb125756e9bbd7a24bed472fa5d96fb5362f","tid":904751,"uid":69484,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"講咁多廢話做咩春 <br />\n果d重要零部件都係外國進口<br />\n根本比人揸春袋 <br />\n利潤都比曬呢d零部件生產商 <br />\n<br />\n中國邊到黎既自信？"},{"pid":"ea9bd6562df6e468cccaa89a3747a2c05b0e4f2f","tid":904751,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc9b96c04feb025987e7857c9ce893276c03114b","tid":904751,"uid":115452,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"比美國睇=冇所謂 因為佢地唔會搞到我<br />\n比中國睇=<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚有所謂</span>"},{"pid":"353a167a5e29155f282a19834716289b6e47c4a7","tid":904751,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"咪諗住隔一排就出黎洗底啦五毛<br />\n永遠唔用支那野"},{"pid":"c448f80b54e8d183b5b65bb6f31a14008527a1ed","tid":904751,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"習大人：而家歐洲嗰邊開始多人用華為啦，華為你地要繼續努力啊&hellip;<br />\n華為發言人：係嘅，習大人<br />\n<br />\n習大人：另外oneplus有好多連登仔用緊，個post入面仲要係正當討論而唔係圍屌，我非常滿意，記住加強產品質素。咁就會令更多連登仔用，可以方便監控。<br />\noneplus發言人：我地會加強隱藏監控程式更難被發現，咁就可以令連登仔繼續用我地部電話啦<br />\n<br />\n習大人：你地兩個都做得非常好&hellip;&hellip;哈哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4a23b4d3b85d7a25e0a9ff364cdb0f4a78afd0","tid":904751,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}